{"tid":818977,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"殘到仆街酒店疑開天殺價！東涌$12,000住兩晚 貴平日4倍","createTime":"2018-09-14T12:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T13:42:51.000Z","uid":23707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ea077f1764de7a25ba292282598cba0ef13dc3b4","tid":818977,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T12:53:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180914&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58682663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180914%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58682663&d=wpkqGnotLFXjRJu74z6Y4sP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=ed5b17da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180914%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58682663&h=082d9ce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180914&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58682663</a><br />\n【超強颱風逼港】酒店疑開天殺價！東涌$12,000住兩晚 貴平日4倍"},{"pid":"b4258ed5092a13dafc845405afe942816d68e927","tid":818977,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T12:53:35.000Z","msg":"超強颱風逼近，不少住在低窪地區、當風或易受風暴潮威脅的市民，或考慮在酒店暫住。惟有酒店開價較平常日子高達4倍，於打風天入住2晚索價12,000元。《蘋果》<a href=\"http://記者於預訂酒店的網站Booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%96%BC%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%82%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99Booking.com&d=wpkqGnotLFXjRJu74z6Y4sP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=403a7aab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">記者於預訂酒店的網站Booking.com</a>搜尋香港諾富特東薈城酒店Novotel於9月15至9月17日的高級間時，發現2晚房價高達12,000元。記者再嘗試搜尋9月22至9月24同一房間的價錢時，2晚房價只需約3,600至4,200元，於颱風天入住該酒店貴了接近4倍。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者以顧客身份致電Novotel前台，接線職員確認上述價錢，當記者追問為何貴了4倍時，職員僅表示因該房間快將額滿，且房價會因應不同時間而有所調整，惟沒提及是否跟颱風有關。<br />\n<br />\n面對來勢洶洶的山竹，居住大嶼山的何小姐對《蘋果》表示，由於住在梅窩碼頭附近，面對大海，前面無遮擋物，每次刮大風，家中的玻璃窗等都被吹到彎曲，隨時有爆玻璃的危險。她擔心山竹會對家人的人生安全造成影響，計劃到酒店暫住：「我哋屋企屬開放式，面積不大，一旦爆玻璃兼強風吹擊，避無可避！」但東涌Novotel兩晚房價太貴，正計劃轉到中環一帶酒店暫住。"},{"pid":"c95fd5a792bb6c08e8fbd16b6445e8cbc069a520","tid":818977,"uid":91813,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T12:54:45.000Z","msg":"supply demand"},{"pid":"97a6df8fe26ac424e4161994067ea812fd0443e8","tid":818977,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T12:58:26.000Z","msg":"職員僅表示因該房間快將額滿<br />\n吹大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f79506447284ada9b2a49bdba4af00731e9e941","tid":818977,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97a6df8fe26ac424e4161994067ea812fd0443e8","tid":818977,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T12:58:26.000Z","msg":"職員僅表示因該房間快將額滿<br />\n吹大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5955464b846f4a60d47feabd77562c049891b9","tid":818977,"uid":26770,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:01:26.000Z","msg":"日本連生意都唔做,開放比當地日本人借住<br />\n<br />\n高下立見<br />\n<br />\n香港崇日係正確,因為大和民族實在係優秀<br />\n去日本一定要如同去朝聖,一言一行要注意<br />\n<br />\n係野蠻國度往先進國家學習的過程"},{"pid":"554ae9a5e5b292631e02bddd425b4913cb33c9aa","tid":818977,"uid":20362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"反正都係住 點解唔住遠啲 要住啲咁食風既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88ddb66c92f64158a8b37a5381e40287c2c610b","tid":818977,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"554ae9a5e5b292631e02bddd425b4913cb33c9aa","tid":818977,"uid":20362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"反正都係住 點解唔住遠啲 要住啲咁食風既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 